cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.LO, cs.CC. 

The paper deals with regular languages and automata, which are fundamental concepts in formal language theory (cs.FL). The linear time verification algorithm mentioned in the abstract suggests that the paper may involve data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.CC). The use of base b and the mention of log(n) suggest that the paper may involve information theory (cs.IT) and possibly also some aspects of computational complexity theory (cs.LO).
